trans-unit.source: Provides information about a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control that you can display in a catalog of Web Parts controls without having to create an instance of the control.
trans-unit.target: Gir informasjon om en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll som du kan vise i en katalog med webdeler kontroller uten å opprette en forekomst av kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: When <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls are displayed in a catalog of controls that users can add to a page, some basic information about each control is required.
trans-unit.target: Når <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller vises i en katalog med kontroller som brukere kan legge til en side, grunnleggende informasjon om hver kontroll kreves.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: For example, it is useful to have a title for the control, and a description, so that as users view a catalog they have enough information to decide whether to add a control to the page.
trans-unit.target: Det er for eksempel nyttig å ha en tittel for kontrollen, og en beskrivelse, slik at brukere vise en katalog har nok informasjon til å bestemme om du vil legge til en kontroll på siden.

trans-unit.source: However, a catalog of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls can potentially contain many controls, and it could affect the performance of an application if an instance of every <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control must be created to extract the information to display in the catalog.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid en katalog med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller kan inneholde mange kontroller, og den kan påvirke ytelsen til et program hvis en forekomst av hver <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen må opprettes for å hente informasjonen som skal vises i katalogen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription class exists so that it is not necessary to create an instance of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control to retrieve the information about the control that is displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDescription finnes slik at det ikke er nødvendig å opprette en forekomst av en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen for å hente informasjon om kontrollen som vises i en katalog for kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: In the Web Parts control set, a WebPartDescription object is also used in conjunction with the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls when a page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: I webdeler kontrollen settet en WebPartDescription objektet også brukes sammen med de ulike <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>Kontroller når en side i katalogen viser modus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription class has two overloads of its constructor, one that takes a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control as a parameter when an instance is available (the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A> constructor), and one that takes several strings with information about the control as parameters (the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A> constructor).
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDescription har to overlastingene av konstruktøren det tar et <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen som en parameter når en forekomst er tilgjengelig (den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A>konstruktøren), og det tar flere strenger med informasjon om kontrollen som parametere (den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A>konstruktøren).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription class also has several properties designed to contain the description information for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartDescription også har flere egenskaper som er utformet for å inneholde informasjonen beskrivelse for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The following table summarizes the WebPartDescription properties, and what property each one corresponds to in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen nedenfor viser egenskapene WebPartDescription, og hvilke egenskapen hver én tilsvarer i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: |Description property|Related part control property| |--------------------------|-----------------------------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID%2A>|<xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title%2A>|<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Title%2A>| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description%2A>|<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A>| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>|<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>|
trans-unit.target: | Description-egenskapen | Relaterte del kontrollegenskapen | |--------------------------|-----------------------------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID%2A>| <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A>| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title%2A>| <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Title%2A>| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description%2A>| <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A>| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>| <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A>|</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Title%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A></xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the class when a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control instance is available.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av klassen når en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen forekomst er tilgjengelig.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription constructor is used for creating a new <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object based on an existing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren WebPartDescription brukes til å opprette en ny <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt basert på en eksisterende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: This constructor simply calls the other overload, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29> constructor, obtaining the required parameter values from properties on the `part` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren kaller ganske enkelt den andre overbelastningen av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29>konstruktøren henting nødvendige parameterverdiene av egenskaper på den `part` parameteren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.%23ctor%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.String%29>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control whose information is contained in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll med informasjon som finnes i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The property of part is or an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Den for part er eller en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the class by using several strings that contain description information for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av klassen ved hjelp av flere strenger som inneholder informasjon om beskrivelse for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescription constructor is used to create a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> class when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is not available.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren WebPartDescription brukes til å opprette en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>klasse når en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>er ikke tilgjengelig.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: For example, this occurs in the case of an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control when it imports a description file for a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel dette skjer med en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>kontrollerer når den importerer beskrivelse filer for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: It gets the information it needs to create a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object directly from the description file, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> instance is not present.
trans-unit.target: Det blir nødvendig informasjon for å opprette en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objekt direkte fra Beskrivelse-fil og en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>forekomsten finnes ikke.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: The value to assign to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID*>.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som skal tilordnes til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.ID*>

trans-unit.source: The value to assign to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title*>.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som skal tilordnes til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Title*>

trans-unit.source: The value to assign to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description*>.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som skal tilordnes til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.Description*>

trans-unit.source: The value to assign to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl*>.
trans-unit.target: Verdien som skal tilordnes til <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl*>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription.CatalogIconImageUrl*>

trans-unit.source: id or title is or an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: ideller title er eller en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets a URL containing the path to an image used as an icon for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter en URL-adresse som inneholder banen til et bilde som brukes som et ikon for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The CatalogIconImageUrl property corresponds directly to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen CatalogIconImageUrl samsvarer med direkte til det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.CatalogIconImageUrl%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If that property is set on a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, then the property in the corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object will also have a value.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne egenskapen er angitt for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen, og deretter egenskapen i den tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objektet har også en verdi.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The CatalogIconImageUrl property applies only when a page is in catalog display mode, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is being displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen CatalogIconImageUrl gjelder bare når en side er i katalogen visningsmodus og en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen vises i en katalog for kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If the control has an icon assigned to it in the property value, the icon appears in the catalog next to the control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis kontrollen har et ikon som er knyttet til den i egenskapsverdien, vises ikonet i katalogen ved siden av kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains a URL; the default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder en URL-adresse. Standardverdien er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets the text of a description for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter teksten i en beskrivelse for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The Description property corresponds directly to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen Beskrivelse samsvarer med direkte til det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.Part.Description%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If that property is set on a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, then the property in the corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object will also have a value.
trans-unit.target: Hvis denne egenskapen er angitt for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen, og deretter egenskapen i den tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>objektet har også en verdi.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The Description property applies only when a page is in catalog display mode, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is being displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Description-egenskapen gjelder bare når en side er i katalogen visningsmodus og en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen vises i en katalog for kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If the control has a description assigned to it, the description appears in the catalog as a ToolTip on the control.
trans-unit.target: Hvis kontrollen har en beskrivelse som er tilordnet, vises beskrivelsen i katalogen som et verktøytips i kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the description for a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control; the default value is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder en beskrivelse for en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroll; standard verdi er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets the ID of a corresponding <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter IDen til en tilsvarende <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The value of the ID property cannot be `null`; it must always have a value.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for ID-egenskapen kan ikke `null`; må alltid ha en verdi.

trans-unit.source: The ID property corresponds directly to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: ID-egenskapen samsvarer med direkte til det <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.ID%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The ID property applies only when a page is in catalog display mode, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is being displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: ID-egenskapen gjelder bare når en side er i katalogen visningsmodus og en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen vises i en katalog for kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the ID of the control.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder IDen for kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Gets the title text of a corresponding <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Henter tittelteksten for en tilsvarende <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The value of the Title property corresponds directly to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for egenskapen tittel samsvarer med direkte til det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Whatever the corresponding <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control has for its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A> property, that becomes the value of the Title property; otherwise, the title is a calculated value.
trans-unit.target: Det tilsvarende <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen har den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A>egenskapen som blir verdien for egenskapen tittel, ellers tittelen er en beregnet verdi.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.DisplayTitle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The Title property applies only when a page is in catalog display mode, and a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control is being displayed in a catalog of controls.
trans-unit.target: Tittel-egenskapen gjelder bare når en side er i katalogen visningsmodus og en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen vises i en katalog for kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: Whatever title is assigned to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control appears next to the control in the catalog.
trans-unit.target: Hvilket som helst tittel er tilordnet til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontrollen vises neste kontrollen i katalogen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the title of the corresponding control.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder tittelen på den tilsvarende kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The default value is a calculated string supplied by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: Standardverdien er en beregnet streng ble levert av .NET Framework.
